<h1>Run Builder</h1>

<p>This tool allows you to describe and assign input files to a
pipeline in order to execute a run.</p>

<p>Your progress will be saved, and you can return to building your
run at any time by clicking on 'My Run Builders' under the 'Results'
entry in the navigation bar.</p>

<p>Before you select your input files, you must choose a name to
distinguish this run.. You may also provide an optional
description.</p>

